Chapter: Multi Lambda In Record

 Probe for the C# emitter curried-type vs uncurried-lambda mismatch.
 A record field typed `Integer -> Integer -> Integer -> Integer` is
 `Func<long, Func<long, Func<long, long>>>` in the emitted C#. A lambda
 `\a b c -> a + b + c` was emitted as `(long a, long b, long c) => ...`,
 which does not match the curried delegate (CS1593).

Section: Types
  Triple = record {
    op : Integer -> Integer -> Integer -> Integer
  }

Section: Entry Point
  main : [Console] Nothing
  main =
   let t = Triple {
    op = \a b c -> a + b + c
   }
   in print-line (integer-to-text (t.op 1 2 3))
